<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Quota exceeded</title>
<style>
body {
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
  background-color: #F8F8F8;;
  color: #000;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center; /* Center horizontally */
  align-items: center; /* Center vertically */
  height: 100vh; /* Make body full height of viewport */
}

.container {
  max-width: 500px;
  margin: 40px auto;
  padding: 30px;
  background-color: #ffffff;
  border-radius: 10px;
  /* box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); */
}

h1 {
  /* text-align: center; */
  color: #2A86FF;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  margin-top: 20px;
  font-size: 35px;
}

p {
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: rgba(19, 36, 65, 0.56);
}

ul {
  padding-left: 20px;
}

a {
   color: #2A86FF;
  text-decoration: none;
}

li {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.logo {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

a:hover {
  text-decoration: underline;
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .container {
    margin: 30px;
    padding: 40px;
  }
  p {
    font-size: 16px;
  }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
 <div class = "logo">
    <a href="https://linksquared.io"><%= image_tag "logo-large-black.svg", alt: "linksquared - logo" %></a>
  </div>
  <p>Quota exceeded. This means that you have reached the limit of free usage for the current period.
  To continue using our services without interruption, upgrade your plan.</p>
 
</div>

</body>
</html>